value: SE Colombia to ne Ecuador, e Peru and w-cent. Amazonian Brazil

Southeastern Colombia in Comisaria de Putumayo (Umbria); north- eastern Peru in Department of Loreto (Sarayacu; Apayacu; Orosa; Rio Yavari); western Brazil on the Rio Solimoes (Sao Paulo de Olivenga; Tonantins).
